* Reduction of technical losses and increase of efficiency;
* Special attention to improve collection rate and commercial profitability;
* Reduction of fraud and theft of electricity;
* Obtaining better conditions in the PPA contracts with private producers, taking into account the interests of both parties.
* Support for more efficient use of charcoal and fuel wood;
* Reforestation of strategic areas for safety of population, environmental protection and tourism;
* Generation of energetic forests;
